1️⃣ Role Management Interface

Design and implement the UI for managing user roles, including role creation, modification, permission assignment, and role-based visibility controls.

2️⃣ RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) Management Module

Build a frontend interface to configure, manage, and monitor RAG data sources, including adding, updating, and organizing knowledge inputs.

3️⃣ General Settings Configuration Panel

Develop a centralized settings page to manage application-level configurations with structured sections, validation handling, and user-friendly controls.

4️⃣ Confluence & Jira Integration Management

Create an integration management interface for configuring, connecting, and maintaining external tools such as Confluence and Jira, including authentication setup and status visibility.
